<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Booking Confirmation</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 10px;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }

        .container {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 30px 80px 80px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            /* box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); */
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .logo {
            height: 50px;
            width: 100%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;

        }

        .logo img {
            height: 100%;
            width: 50px;
        }

        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .header p {
            font-size: 14px;
            margin: 5px 0px;
        }

        table,
        th,
        td {
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            font-size: 12px;
        }

        th,
        td {
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: left;
        }

        th {
            background-color: #f2f2f2;
        }



        .details {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .details h3 {
            color: #000000;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .details p {
            color: #000000;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin: 5px 0;
        }

        .footer p {
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            margin-top: 0px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">

        <div class="logo">
            <img src="https://tiptop-stag.syd1.digitaloceanspaces.com/staging/TiptopUser.png" alt="">
        </div>
        <br />
        <div class="header">
            <p>Dear {{{name}}},</p><br />
            <p>To verify your email address, please enter the following verification
                code:</p>
            <h3>{{{otp}}}</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="details">
            <p>NOTE: This verification code will expire after 5 minutes.</p>
            <p>If you experience any difficulties, please contact us immediately.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer" style="margin-top: 50px;">
            <p>Regards,</p>
            <p>TipTop Ride (TipTop Transport Solutions)</p>
            <p>Quality, Trusted & Professional.</p>
            <p>Branch and Base: Mascot, Sydney, NSW, Australia.</p>
            <p>24/7 Contact Numbers : 02 96699390 (LOCALS), +61296699390 (INTERNATIONAL)</p>
            <p>TipTop Transport Solutions PTY LTD Â© All Rights Reserved.2025</p>
        </div>

    </div>
</body>

</html>